In a statement issued on January 27, 2017, the speaker expresses deep sadness and pays tribute to the victims, survivors, and heroes of the Holocaust. They acknowledge the unimaginable suffering inflicted by Nazi terror but also highlight the resilience and courage demonstrated during this dark period. The speaker expresses gratitude towards those who risked their lives to save innocent people. They vow to use their position and influence to prevent evil from triumphing over good, and to promote love and tolerance worldwide.